<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bài viết mới từ {{authorName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #a855f7 100%);
            padding: 32px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .header .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 36px 30px;
        }
        .author-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .author-avatar {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-right: 12px;
        }
        .author-info .name {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1f2937;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .author-info .label {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
        .post-card {
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .post-thumbnail {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
        }
        .post-thumbnail-placeholder {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0e7ff 0%, #f3e8ff 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 48px;
        }
        .post-body {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .post-category {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e0e7ff;
            color: #6366f1;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .post-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .post-description {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin: 0;
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .cta-wrapper {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 28px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #a855f7 100%);
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }
        .unsubscribe-note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 24px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #6366f1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="badge">📰 Bài viết mới</div>
            <h1>Người bạn theo dõi vừa đăng bài!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p style="color: #4b5563; margin-top: 0;">Xin chào <strong>{{recipientName}}</strong>,</p>

            <div class="author-row">
                <div class="author-avatar">{{authorInitial}}</div>
                <div class="author-info">
                    <div class="name">{{authorName}}</div>
                    <div class="label">Người bạn đang theo dõi</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0;">
                <strong style="color: #374151;">{{authorName}}</strong> vừa xuất bản một bài viết mới. Đừng bỏ lỡ nhé!
            </p>

            <div class="post-card">
                {{#if thumbnail}}
                <img src="{{thumbnail}}" alt="{{title}}" class="post-thumbnail" />
                {{else}}
                <div class="post-thumbnail-placeholder">📝</div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="post-body">
                    {{#if category}}
                    <span class="post-category">{{category}}</span>
                    {{/if}}
                    <h2 class="post-title">{{title}}</h2>
                    <p class="post-description">{{description}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-wrapper">
                <a href="{{postUrl}}" class="cta-button">Đọc bài viết ngay →</a>
            </div>

            <hr class="divider" />

            <p class="unsubscribe-note">
                Bạn nhận email này vì đang theo dõi <strong>{{authorName}}</strong> trên
                <a href="{{siteUrl}}" style="color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none;">Foxtek Blog</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2024 Foxtek Blog — <a href="{{siteUrl}}">foxtek.blog</a></p>
            <p>TP. Hồ Chí Minh, Việt Nam</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
